title.narrative: Pacific Regional - Support to Secretariat of the Pacific Association of Supreme Audit Institutions

description.narrative: New Zealand's Office of the Auditor General (OAG) supports the Pacific Association of Supreme Audit Institutions (PASAI) Secretariat to deliver the Pacific Regional Audit Initiative (PRAI). The PRAI aims to achieve timely, quality public audits in the Pacific region through training, advocacy and cooperative audits. The OAG provides support to the Secretariat in a range of ways, including administrative support and the contribution of technical expertise to the PRAI.
